PEOPLE of the State of Michigan, Plaintiff-Appellee,
v.
Ronald Lee FOSTER, Defendant-Appellant. SC: 156088
COA: 336811 Supreme Court of Michigan. September 27, 2018

Order

On order of the Court, the motion for reconsideration of this Court's March 21, 2018 order is considered, and it is DENIED, because it does not appear that the order was entered erroneously.
